		}
		{
			dependencies: ["083CFC179D001044"]
			description: [
				"&6&oAmong the ruins, old scribes left a warning: \"Those who conquer the three elements of the mighty scales may yet prove worthy to face the Warden.\" The meaning is clear enough. Three dragons guard the path ahead.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"Slay the elemental dragons and turn their scales into armor worthy of the hunt.\"&r&r"
