		{
			dependencies: ["4AB16D387D6EC80E"]
			description: [
				"&6&oThe corruption that reached the land has also stirred the seas. Ancient waters have been disturbed, and from the deep has risen a one-eyed creature that now terrorizes the fishermen who still brave the coast.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"Another relic of the old world has gone hostile. The deep will not be left untouched.\"&r&r"
