		{
			dependencies: ["60B654D17B7CB092"]
			description: [
				"&6&oVictory never comes without drawing the attention of greater horrors. Now the deserts themselves have become hunting grounds for the Faded One, a thousand-scaled beast whose stealth and blade-like teeth can tear through an army.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"If the sands hide such monsters, then the desert is no longer empty.\"&r&r"
