		{
			dependencies: ["6F83DB86DDEEC3E3"]
			description: [
				"&6&oWith the desert monstrosity defeated, another threat emerges from the otherside of the spectrum. A large body of frost with Yeti-like features not to be confused with his brothers. He sleeps within the cold ice in which he gatekeeps the icy key to the GATE.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"Another one to kill...\".&r&r"
