		{
			dependencies: ["65CB799F7BDA155A"]
			description: [
				"&6&oAs the miasma thickens, judgment itself begins to fail. The Ashlord, once vice general of the dragonborne race, has been corrupted and now rules his castle through an army of the undead. A great bounty has been placed upon his head, and his fall would mark another victory for the Pact.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"Even the strongest can be claimed by the shadow if left unguarded.\"&r&r"
