		{
			dependencies: ["05D47E456E31A632"]
			description: [
				"&6&oAnother ruin, another scribe, another clue. One inscription speaks of a loop to the Undergarden, formed with fourteen stone bricks and a gem catalyst. Whatever this passage was meant to hide, it could lead deeper into the truth.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"The old world left breadcrumbs everywhere. We only need to follow them.\"&r&r"
