		{
			dependencies: ["500788D5D57F78D7"]
			description: [
				"&6&oThe UnderGarden is a grotesque place, full of forms that should never have existed. Yet beneath its corruption lies a world waiting to be uncovered. Whether it offers treasure or death, the only way forward is deeper.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"If the old scribes were right, then the underground still has answers.\"&r&r"
