		{
			dependencies: ["4FF6DE3CD28DABE8"]
			description: [
				"&6&oThe catacombs are not empty. Their halls are guarded by forgotten golems carrying the remnants of the miasma within their stone bodies. Whatever happened here, it twisted even the protectors of the underground.&r&r"
