		{
			dependencies: ["35788DB7EB17912E"]
			description: [
				"&6&oTo perform the soul ritual written in the Undergarden ruins, you must first venture into the fiery depths of the Nether. Only there, within the charred halls of old fortresses, can you claim the cursed skulls of the Withered ones.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"The flames are harsh, but they forge the key to the next battle.\"&r&r"
