			dependencies: ["11EBA947CA6F6434"]
			description: [
				"&o&6As the Wither fell, its tainted power faded with it, and for a time the common people could breathe again. But the miasma still lingers in the deeper dimensions, too vast for a single victory to end. Something far greater will be needed to defeat what remains.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"This was never the final battle. It was only the end of the beginning.\"&r&r"
